        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer890458888" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17522502179218824536">It was an amazing book. Book that I could not let go. Once you start reading it you have to finish. You have no choice. It sucks you into its world.<br/>Excellent plot and amazingly easy to relate to characters. I began to wonder should I do the same as Shane and try to find something I was missing in my own life. Maybe run away to find a place of my dreams. Oh, wouldn&apos;t it be nice to find so many different people that are so eager to help you. Anyhow, I really enjoyed reading it, it was fun, easy to</span>
