<span id="freeTextContainer9469106112321438578">Much like the 1971 movie &quot;Red Sky at Morning&quot; Finding Sagrado captures both the spirit of youth and the beauty of the southwest. The book is poetic in its descriptions of the inherent magic of New Mexico, and there are even some magical/mystical elements in the book. It is a book that connected my heart to the characters, I found myself anticipating and secretly praying for their fates. Highly recommended! </span>
